MODIFICATIONS MADE:

This fork contains the following modifications from the original Solana Web3.js library:

1. BRANDING AND NAMING CHANGES:
   - Changed all references from "Solana" to "Trezoa"
   - Changed cryptocurrency symbol from "SOL" to "TRZ"
   - Changed token standard from "SPL" to "TPL" (Trezoa Program Library)
   - Updated organization names:
     * "Solana Labs" → "Trezoa-team"
     * "Solana Foundation" → "TRZ Ledger Foundation"
     * "Agave Labs" → "Trezoa-team"
     * "Anza" → "Trezoa-team"

2. DOMAIN AND URL CHANGES:
   - solana.com → trezoa.com
   - solana.org → trzledger.org
   - Anza.xyz → trezoa.xyz
   - agave.com → trezoa.xyz
   - Anza.com → trezoa.xyz

3. PACKAGE NAMESPACE CHANGES:
   - Internal packages: @solana/* → @trezoa/*
   - Maintained workspace structure with local dependencies

4. CONTACT INFORMATION:
   - Updated maintainer email: maintainers@trezoa.xyz
   - Updated repository URL: https://github.com/trezoa-xyz/kit
   - Updated issue tracker: https://github.com/trezoa-xyz/kit/issues

5. DOCUMENTATION UPDATES:
   - Updated all README files with Trezoa-specific information
   - Updated API documentation references
   - Updated code examples and snippets

6. CONFIGURATION CHANGES:
   - Updated package.json files with new names and descriptions
   - Updated TypeScript configuration files
   - Updated build scripts and CI/CD configurations
   - Updated explorer URLs to reference Trezoa explorer

